"numbers\", values));\n\n        assertEquals(\"java.lang.Number:1,2,3\", result);\n    }\n\n    public interface ProxyApi {\n        String combineWords(String[] values);\n\n        String describeNumbers(Number[] numbers);\n    }\n\n    public static final class RecordingProxy implements ProxyApi {\n        @Override\n        public String combineWords(String[] values) {\n            return values.getClass().getComponentType().getName() + \":\" + String.join(\"|\", values);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public String describeNumbers(Number[] numbers) {\n            String valueText = List.of(numbers).stream()\n                    .map(String::valueOf)\n                    .collect(Collectors.joining(\",\"));\n            return numbers.getClass().getComponentType().getName() + \":\" + valueText;\n        }\n    }\n\n    private enum TestApiMethod implements ApiMethod {\n        COMBINE_WORDS(\"combineWords\", String.class, List.of(\"values\"), String[].class),\n        DESCRIBE_NUMBERS(\"describeNumbers\", String.class, List.of(\"numbers\"), Number[].class);\n\n        private final String name;\n        private final Class<?> resultType;\n        private final List<String> argNames;\n        private final List<Class<?>> argTypes;\n        private final Method method;\n\n        TestApiMethod(String name, Class<?> resultType, List<String> argNames, Class<?>... argTypes) {\n            this.name = name;\n            this.resultType = resultType;\n            this.argNames = argNames;\n            this.argTypes = List.of(argTypes);\n            this.method = lookupProxyMethod(name, argTypes);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public String getName() {\n            return name;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Class<?> getResultType() {\n            return resultType;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public List<String> getArgNames() {\n            return argNames;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public List<String> getSetterArgNames() {\n            return List.of();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public List<Class<?>> getArgTypes() {\n            return argTypes;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Method getMethod() {\n            return method;\n        }\n\n        private static Method lookupProxyMethod(String name, Class<?>... parameterTypes) {\n            try {\n                return ProxyApi.class.getMethod(name, parameterTypes);\n            } catch (NoSuchMethodException e) {\n                throw new ExceptionInInitializerError(e);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778171970323}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_StO05zB9KApqIfOWucnxE3BC|fc_0a356f2de30f7a220169fcc041e988819f8ff80d94c8f38db4", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage org_apache_camel.camel_support;\n\nimport java.util.LinkedHashMap;\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.Map;\n\nimport org.apache.camel.support.component.ApiMethodArg;\nimport org.apache.camel.support.component.ApiMethodParser;\nimport org.apache.camel.support.component.ApiMethodParser.ApiMethodModel;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n\nimport static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertEquals;\nimport static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertSame;\n\npublic class ApiMethodParserTest {\n    @Test\n    void parsesMethodWithArrayAndNestedClassArguments() {\n        String signature = \"java.lang.String combine(java.lang.String[] names, \"\n                + \"org_apache_camel.camel_support.ApiMethodParserTest.NestedValue value)\";\n        TestApiMethodParser parser = new TestApiMethodParser(ProxyApi.class);\n        parser.setSignatures(List.of(signature));\n        parser.addSignatureArguments(signature, arguments(\n                \"names\", \"java.lang.String[]\",\n                \"value\", \"org_apache_camel.camel_support.ApiMethodParserTest.NestedValue\"));\n\n        List<ApiMethodModel> models = parser.parse();\n\n        assertEquals(1, models.size());\n        ApiMethodModel model = models.get(0);\n        assertEquals(\"COMBINE\", model.getUniqueName());\n        assertEquals(\"combine\", model.getName());\n        assertSame(String.class, model.getResultType());\n        assertEquals(\"combine\", model.getMethod().getName());\n        assertEquals(List.of(String[].class, NestedValue.class), model.getArguments().stream()\n                .map(ApiMethodArg::getType)\n                .toList());\n    }\n\n    private static Map<String, String> arguments(String firstName, String firstType, String secondName, String secondType) {\n        Map<String, String> arguments = new LinkedHashMap<>();\n        arguments.put(firstName, firstType);\n        arguments.put(secondName, secondType);\n        return arguments;\n    }\n\n    public interface ProxyApi {\n        String combine(String[] names, NestedValue value);\n    }\n\n    public static final class NestedValue {\n    }\n\n    private static final class TestApiMethodParser extends ApiMethodParser<ProxyApi> {\n        private TestApiMethodParser(Class<ProxyApi> proxyType) {\n            super(proxyType);\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778171970323}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_jF6sI9RJDcLfz4oncxpWgfRM|fc_0a356f2de30f7a220169fcc041e994819f9e59b059978a9da0", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\nplugins {\n    id \"org.graalvm.internal.tck\"\n}\n\nString libraryVersion = tck.testedLibraryVersion.get()\n\ndependencies {\n    testImplementation \"org.apache.camel: